nodes.name: Organization Export Organization Export Get

timeout.description: Timeout specifies the number of milliseconds before the request times out. If the request takes longer than timeout, the request will be aborted.

id.description: The unique ID of this request.

The type of export requested. One of:

expires.description: The time and date when the request expires.

status.description:

- `failed`
- `in_process`
- `queued`
- `completed`

account_id.description: Select users that are members of the specified account. At least one of `email`, `account_id` or `organization_reserved_domain_id` must be specified.

metadata_url.description: A pre-configured GET request to get the status of the export. Generally this is the same URI used to access this endpoint.

percent_completed.description: An integer between 0 to 100 (inclusive) that reports the progress of the request.

number_rows.description: The number of rows returned in this request.

size_bytes.description: The size of the request in bytes.

id.description: The unique ID of the task request.

site_id.description: The ID of the site the response is for.

url.description: The URL that returns the results as a CSV text stream.

number_rows.description: The number of rows returned in the result.

size_bytes.description: The size of the response in bytes.
